FBIS3-35835 "drsov021_b_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-021 Document Type:Daily Report 1 Feb 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Confirms Security Council Members LD0102103594 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1000 GMT 1 Feb 94 LD0102103594 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Russian President Boris Yeltsin today signed an edict on the members of the Russian Security Council. The presidential press service reports that the council's members are confirmed in their posts. They are federal counterintelligence service director Nikolay Galushko, Defense Minister Pavel Grachev, Interior Minister Viktor Yerin, Justice Minister Yuriy Kalmykov, Foreign Minister Andrey Kozyrev, and also Foreign Intelligence Service Director Yevgeniy Primakov, Sergey Shakhray, nationalities and regional policy minister, and Sergey Shoygu, civil defense and emergency situations minister.
